abstract: Uber, the San Francisco start-up company, uses a clever algorithm to summon a car quickly with a smartphone app, but it had trouble outmaneuvering the wonky politics of the city of Washington. After six months, the company has finally won a battle with the city, which had tried to deem its service illegal.

headline.main: Uber, Maker of Summon-a-Car App, Wins in Washington
